text:
Blac Chyna, Tyga, and Kylie Jenner

Imagine running into your ex while he's with the new girlfriend that he may or may not have started seeing before he ended things with you. Then imagine that you later have a child with the new girlfriend's brother and end up having to see the whole family all the time. Blac Chyna is a brave woman.
